==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nodose
<hw>No*dose"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>nodosus</ets>, fr. <ets>nodus</ets> knot.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Knotty; having numerous or conspicuous nodes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having nodes or prominences;
having the alternate joints enlarged, as the antennae of certain
insects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nodosity</ent>⟦br⟧
